{
  "verses": [
    {
      "id": 1,
      "verse_number": 1,
      "page_number": 592,
      "verse_key": "88:1",
      "juz_number": 30,
      "hizb_number": 60,
      "rub_el_hizb_number": 237,
      "sajdah_type": null,
      "sajdah_number": null,
      "text": "هَلۡ أَتَىٰكَ حَدِيثُ ٱلۡغَٰشِيَةِ",
      "translation": "（使徒*よ、）圧倒的事態[1]の話は、あなたに届いたか？",
      "footnotes": "[1]　「圧倒的事態」とは、その恐怖で人々を圧倒する、復活の日*のこと（ムヤッサル５９2頁参照）。"
    },
    {
      "id": 2,
      "verse_number": 2,
      "page_number": 592,
      "verse_key": "88:2",
      "juz_number": 30,
      "hizb_number": 60,
      "rub_el_hizb_number": 237,
      "sajdah_type": null,
      "sajdah_number": null,
      "text": "وُجُوهٞ يَوۡمَئِذٍ خَٰشِعَةٌ",
      "translation": "その日、（不信仰者*たちの）顔は、（懲罰への）恐怖に陥っている。",
      "footnotes": ""
    },
    {
      "id": 3,
      "verse_number": 3,
      "page_number": 592,
      "verse_key": "88:3",
      "juz_number": 30,
      "hizb_number": 60,
      "rub_el_hizb_number": 237,
      "sajdah_type": null,
      "sajdah_number": null,
      "text": "عَامِلَةٞ نَّاصِبَةٞ",
      "translation": "（それらの顔は、過酷な）労役に就き、消耗している。",
      "footnotes": ""
    },
    {
      "id": 4,
      "verse_number": 4,
      "page_number": 592,
      "verse_key": "88:4",
      "juz_number": 30,
      "hizb_number": 60,
      "rub_el_hizb_number": 237,
      "sajdah_type": null,
      "sajdah_number": null,
      "text": "تَصۡلَىٰ نَارًا حَامِيَةٗ",
      "translation": "（それらは、）酷熱の業火に入って炙られる。",
      "footnotes": ""
    },
    {
      "id": 5,
      "verse_number": 5,
      "page_number": 592,
      "verse_key": "88:5",
      "juz_number": 30,
      "hizb_number": 60,
      "rub_el_hizb_number": 237,
      "sajdah_type": null,
      "sajdah_number": null,
      "text": "تُسۡقَىٰ مِنۡ عَيۡنٍ ءَانِيَةٖ",
      "translation": "（それらは、）煮えたぎる泉から、飲まされる。[1]",
      "footnotes": "[1]　地獄の民の飲食物については、洞窟章2９、イブラーヒーム*章1６－1７、整列者章６2－６６、サード章５７－５８、煙霧章４３－４６、ムハンマド*章1５、出来事章５2－５５、衣を纏（まと）う 者章1３、真実章３６－３７なども参照。"
    },
    {
      "id": 6,
      "verse_number": 6,
      "page_number": 592,
      "verse_key": "88:6",
      "juz_number": 30,
      "hizb_number": 60,
      "rub_el_hizb_number": 237,
      "sajdah_type": null,
      "sajdah_number": null,
      "text": "لَّيۡسَ لَهُمۡ طَعَامٌ إِلَّا مِن ضَرِيعٖ",
      "translation": "彼らには、忌々しい植物[1]しか、食べ物がない。",
      "footnotes": "[1]　「忌々しい植物」の解釈には、「炎の木」「ザックーム（夜の旅章６０「呪われた木」の訳注を参照）」「棘のある植物の一種」といった諸説がある（イブン・カスィール８：３８５参照）。"
    },
    {
      "id": 7,
      "verse_number": 7,
      "page_number": 592,
      "verse_key": "88:7",
      "juz_number": 30,
      "hizb_number": 60,
      "rub_el_hizb_number": 237,
      "sajdah_type": null,
      "sajdah_number": null,
      "text": "لَّا يُسۡمِنُ وَلَا يُغۡنِي مِن جُوعٖ",
      "translation": "（それらは彼らを）太らせもしなければ、（彼らの）飢えを満たしてもくれない。",
      "footnotes": ""
    },
    {
      "id": 8,
      "verse_number": 8,
      "page_number": 592,
      "verse_key": "88:8",
      "juz_number": 30,
      "hizb_number": 60,
      "rub_el_hizb_number": 237,
      "sajdah_type": null,
      "sajdah_number": null,
      "text": "وُجُوهٞ يَوۡمَئِذٖ نَّاعِمَةٞ",
      "translation": "（復活の）その日、（信仰者たちの）顔は、恩恵を享受している。",
      "footnotes": ""
    },
    {
      "id": 9,
      "verse_number": 9,
      "page_number": 592,
      "verse_key": "88:9",
      "juz_number": 30,
      "hizb_number": 60,
      "rub_el_hizb_number": 237,
      "sajdah_type": null,
      "sajdah_number": null,
      "text": "لِّسَعۡيِهَا رَاضِيَةٞ",
      "translation": "（それらは、）自分たちの（現世で行った）努力（への褒美）ゆえに満足している、",
      "footnotes": ""
    },
    {
      "id": 10,
      "verse_number": 10,
      "page_number": 592,
      "verse_key": "88:10",
      "juz_number": 30,
      "hizb_number": 60,
      "rub_el_hizb_number": 237,
      "sajdah_type": null,
      "sajdah_number": null,
      "text": "فِي جَنَّةٍ عَالِيَةٖ",
      "translation": "高き楽園の中で。",
      "footnotes": ""
    },
    {
      "id": 11,
      "verse_number": 11,
      "page_number": 592,
      "verse_key": "88:11",
      "juz_number": 30,
      "hizb_number": 60,
      "rub_el_hizb_number": 237,
      "sajdah_type": null,
      "sajdah_number": null,
      "text": "لَّا تَسۡمَعُ فِيهَا لَٰغِيَةٗ",
      "translation": "（それらは、）そこで戯言[1]を耳にすることもない。",
      "footnotes": "[1]　「戯言については、信仰者たち章３の同語の訳注を参照（アッ＝サアディー９21頁参照）。"
    },
    {
      "id": 12,
      "verse_number": 12,
      "page_number": 592,
      "verse_key": "88:12",
      "juz_number": 30,
      "hizb_number": 60,
      "rub_el_hizb_number": 237,
      "sajdah_type": null,
      "sajdah_number": null,
      "text": "فِيهَا عَيۡنٞ جَارِيَةٞ",
      "translation": "そこには、流れる泉がある。",
      "footnotes": ""
    },
    {
      "id": 13,
      "verse_number": 13,
      "page_number": 592,
      "verse_key": "88:13",
      "juz_number": 30,
      "hizb_number": 60,
      "rub_el_hizb_number": 237,
      "sajdah_type": null,
      "sajdah_number": null,
      "text": "فِيهَا سُرُرٞ مَّرۡفُوعَةٞ",
      "translation": "そこには、高い寝台がある。",
      "footnotes": ""
    },
    {
      "id": 14,
      "verse_number": 14,
      "page_number": 592,
      "verse_key": "88:14",
      "juz_number": 30,
      "hizb_number": 60,
      "rub_el_hizb_number": 237,
      "sajdah_type": null,
      "sajdah_number": null,
      "text": "وَأَكۡوَابٞ مَّوۡضُوعَةٞ",
      "translation": "また、配置された杯、",
      "footnotes": ""
    },
    {
      "id": 15,
      "verse_number": 15,
      "page_number": 592,
      "verse_key": "88:15",
      "juz_number": 30,
      "hizb_number": 60,
      "rub_el_hizb_number": 237,
      "sajdah_type": null,
      "sajdah_number": null,
      "text": "وَنَمَارِقُ مَصۡفُوفَةٞ",
      "translation": "並べられた肘掛け、",
      "footnotes": ""
    },
    {
      "id": 16,
      "verse_number": 16,
      "page_number": 592,
      "verse_key": "88:16",
      "juz_number": 30,
      "hizb_number": 60,
      "rub_el_hizb_number": 237,
      "sajdah_type": null,
      "sajdah_number": null,
      "text": "وَزَرَابِيُّ مَبۡثُوثَةٌ",
      "translation": "敷き広げられた絨毯がある。",
      "footnotes": ""
    },
    {
      "id": 17,
      "verse_number": 17,
      "page_number": 592,
      "verse_key": "88:17",
      "juz_number": 30,
      "hizb_number": 60,
      "rub_el_hizb_number": 237,
      "sajdah_type": null,
      "sajdah_number": null,
      "text": "أَفَلَا يَنظُرُونَ إِلَى ٱلۡإِبِلِ كَيۡفَ خُلِقَتۡ",
      "translation": "一体、彼ら（不信仰者*たち）は、ラクダがいかに創られたのか、見て（考え）ないのか？",
      "footnotes": ""
    },
    {
      "id": 18,
      "verse_number": 18,
      "page_number": 592,
      "verse_key": "88:18",
      "juz_number": 30,
      "hizb_number": 60,
      "rub_el_hizb_number": 237,
      "sajdah_type": null,
      "sajdah_number": null,
      "text": "وَإِلَى ٱلسَّمَآءِ كَيۡفَ رُفِعَتۡ",
      "translation": "また天が、いかに上げられたのかを？",
      "footnotes": ""
    },
    {
      "id": 19,
      "verse_number": 19,
      "page_number": 592,
      "verse_key": "88:19",
      "juz_number": 30,
      "hizb_number": 60,
      "rub_el_hizb_number": 237,
      "sajdah_type": null,
      "sajdah_number": null,
      "text": "وَإِلَى ٱلۡجِبَالِ كَيۡفَ نُصِبَتۡ",
      "translation": "また、山々がいかに据え付けられたのかを？",
      "footnotes": ""
    },
    {
      "id": 20,
      "verse_number": 20,
      "page_number": 592,
      "verse_key": "88:20",
      "juz_number": 30,
      "hizb_number": 60,
      "rub_el_hizb_number": 237,
      "sajdah_type": null,
      "sajdah_number": null,
      "text": "وَإِلَى ٱلۡأَرۡضِ كَيۡفَ سُطِحَتۡ",
      "translation": "また、大地がいかに平坦に伸ばされたかを？",
      "footnotes": ""
    },
    {
      "id": 21,
      "verse_number": 21,
      "page_number": 592,
      "verse_key": "88:21",
      "juz_number": 30,
      "hizb_number": 60,
      "rub_el_hizb_number": 237,
      "sajdah_type": null,
      "sajdah_number": null,
      "text": "فَذَكِّرۡ إِنَّمَآ أَنتَ مُذَكِّرٞ",
      "translation": "ならば（使徒*よ、人々に、啓示で）教訓を与えよ。あなたは教訓を与える者でしかないのだから。",
      "footnotes": ""
    },
    {
      "id": 22,
      "verse_number": 22,
      "page_number": 592,
      "verse_key": "88:22",
      "juz_number": 30,
      "hizb_number": 60,
      "rub_el_hizb_number": 237,
      "sajdah_type": null,
      "sajdah_number": null,
      "text": "لَّسۡتَ عَلَيۡهِم بِمُصَيۡطِرٍ",
      "translation": "あなたは、彼らに対（して信仰へと無理強い）する制圧者などではない。",
      "footnotes": ""
    },
    {
      "id": 23,
      "verse_number": 23,
      "page_number": 592,
      "verse_key": "88:23",
      "juz_number": 30,
      "hizb_number": 60,
      "rub_el_hizb_number": 237,
      "sajdah_type": null,
      "sajdah_number": null,
      "text": "إِلَّا مَن تَوَلَّىٰ وَكَفَرَ",
      "translation": "但し、（教訓に）背を向け、不信仰（の固執）に陥った者は別で、",
      "footnotes": ""
    },
    {
      "id": 24,
      "verse_number": 24,
      "page_number": 592,
      "verse_key": "88:24",
      "juz_number": 30,
      "hizb_number": 60,
      "rub_el_hizb_number": 237,
      "sajdah_type": null,
      "sajdah_number": null,
      "text": "فَيُعَذِّبُهُ ٱللَّهُ ٱلۡعَذَابَ ٱلۡأَكۡبَرَ",
      "translation": "アッラー*は彼を（、業火という）最大の懲罰で罰される。",
      "footnotes": ""
    },
    {
      "id": 25,
      "verse_number": 25,
      "page_number": 592,
      "verse_key": "88:25",
      "juz_number": 30,
      "hizb_number": 60,
      "rub_el_hizb_number": 237,
      "sajdah_type": null,
      "sajdah_number": null,
      "text": "إِنَّ إِلَيۡنَآ إِيَابَهُمۡ",
      "translation": "本当にわれら*にこそ、彼らの（死後の）帰り所があるのだから。",
      "footnotes": ""
    },
    {
      "id": 26,
      "verse_number": 26,
      "page_number": 592,
      "verse_key": "88:26",
      "juz_number": 30,
      "hizb_number": 60,
      "rub_el_hizb_number": 237,
      "sajdah_type": null,
      "sajdah_number": null,
      "text": "ثُمَّ إِنَّ عَلَيۡنَا حِسَابَهُم",
      "translation": "それから、本当にわれら*にこそ、彼らの（行いの）清算が委ねられているのだから。",
      "footnotes": ""
    }
  ]
}